content:
Really liked this game until my son got to the hamster preschool level and 
it kept shutting itself off! Please help fix this!!!
Best game for tots out there while making learning fun. Lots of fun activities, especially the racing hamsters!
Very easy for young children of today. The controls are simple. My three-year-old loves it!
My boys love it! (ages 2, 4 and 6) one said " I love the race hamsters!! I love it! I love it! I love it! Everyday I want to play the Hampster game!!"
Perfect! Easy to play and great for kids!
Great for my kids learning to read
My kids love each word game. The ice cream one is their favorite.
